# Intention Source

This directory is editable source material for `${loop_dir_name}`.

## Role

- Keep the loop objective, participants, operating model, constraints, and open questions here.
- Edit these files directly when the loop intent changes.
- Treat `../execplan/` as generated operational material derived from this source area.

## Conventions

- `loop-overview.md` is the entrypoint.
- `project-context.md` is created by `init` when project or codebase context capture is needed.
- Add narrower Markdown files only when they make the intent easier to edit.
- Preserve uncertainty explicitly instead of inventing missing policy.
